(self.webpackChunk_N_E=self.webpackChunk_N_E||[]).push([[4454],{64454:function(e){"use strict";e.exports=JSON.parse("{\"md\":\"# Core Actions\\n\\n## Introduction\\n\\nCore Actions are pre-defined Platform Actions that are provided by the Scale8 Platform. This is similar to the list of actions provided by Google Tag Manager and Tag Manager offerings such as Abobe DTM.\\n\\n## Create Hidden iFrame\\n\\nThis action will create a custom hidden iFrame. It is commonly used to load another library or sync pixels.\\n\\n### Configuration Properties\\n\\n| Property&nbsp;Name | Property&nbsp;Description | Var&nbsp;Type | Default&nbsp;Value | Is&nbsp;Required |\\n|---|---|---|---|---|\\n| url | iFrame URL that will be called by the action. | STRING |  | Yes |\\n| use_cache_buster | By default enabled. It will add a random parameter to the end of the provided iFrame URL to prevent caching. | STRING | Enabled | No |\\n| start_date | Optional start date | DATETIME |  | No |\\n| end_date | Optional end date | DATETIME |  | No |\\n\\n## Custom HTML\\n\\nTakes a block of custom HTML and will load it via an iframe inside of the requested tag\\n\\n### Configuration Properties\\n\\n| Property&nbsp;Name | Property&nbsp;Description | Var&nbsp;Type | Default&nbsp;Value | Is&nbsp;Required |\\n|---|---|---|---|---|\\n| html | Raw HTML block that will be rendered into it's own frame | STRING |  | Yes |\\n\\n## Custom JavaScript\\n\\nTakes a block of custom JavaScript and will load it via an iframe inside of the requested tag\\n\\n### Configuration Properties\\n\\n| Property&nbsp;Name | Property&nbsp;Description | Var&nbsp;Type | Default&nbsp;Value | Is&nbsp;Required |\\n|---|---|---|---|---|\\n| js | Raw JavaScript that will be executed in it's own frame | STRING |  | Yes |\\n\\n## Fire Image Pixel\\n\\nThis action will create a custom hidden image tag used to trigger a tracking pixel.\\n\\n### Configuration Properties\\n\\n| Property&nbsp;Name | Property&nbsp;Description | Var&nbsp;Type | Default&nbsp;Value | Is&nbsp;Required |\\n|---|---|---|---|---|\\n| image_url | Image URL that will be called by the action. | STRING |  | Yes |\\n| use_cache_buster | By default enabled. It will add a random parameter to the end of the provided image URL to prevent caching. | STRING | Enabled | No |\\n| start_date | Optional start date | DATETIME |  | No |\\n| end_date | Optional end date | DATETIME |  | No |\\n\\n## Increment App-State Variable\\n\\nThis action will increment the value of the key provided. If the value doesn't exist it will be set to 1, otherwise it will be incremented\\n\\n### Configuration Properties\\n\\n| Property&nbsp;Name | Property&nbsp;Description | Var&nbsp;Type | Default&nbsp;Value | Is&nbsp;Required |\\n|---|---|---|---|---|\\n| key | Dot notation supported key. e.g. 'a.b.c' | STRING |  | Yes |\\n| page_only | If page only is set to 'Yes' then anything set will only persist while user remains on the page. Otherwise if 'No' it will persist via local storage and can be referenced on subsequent page loads. For single page applications, if the navigation changes this will wipe any page state data. | STRING | Yes | No |\\n\\n## Inject Script\\n\\nThis action will inject a script into the page. This is commonly used to load another third party library.\\n\\n### Configuration Properties\\n\\n| Property&nbsp;Name | Property&nbsp;Description | Var&nbsp;Type | Default&nbsp;Value | Is&nbsp;Required |\\n|---|---|---|---|---|\\n| url | Script URL that will be called by the action. | STRING |  | Yes |\\n| use_cache_buster | By default enabled. It will add a random parameter to the end of the provided URL to prevent caching. | STRING | Enabled | No |\\n| start_date | Optional start date | DATETIME |  | No |\\n| end_date | Optional end date | DATETIME |  | No |\\n\\n## Set App-State Variable\\n\\nThis action will create a custom hidden image tag used to trigger a tracking pixel.\\n\\n### Configuration Properties\\n\\n| Property&nbsp;Name | Property&nbsp;Description | Var&nbsp;Type | Default&nbsp;Value | Is&nbsp;Required |\\n|---|---|---|---|---|\\n| key | Dot notation supported key. e.g. 'a.b.c' | STRING |  | Yes |\\n| value | Only string values are currently supported, although more support for other variable types will be added soon. | STRING |  | Yes |\\n| page_only | If page only is set to 'Yes' then anything set will only persist while user remains on the page. Otherwise if 'No' it will persist via local storage and can be referenced on subsequent page loads. For single page applications, if the navigation changes this will wipe any page state data. | STRING | Yes | No |\\n\\n## Simple Logger\\n\\nThis action will log a message to the debug console\\n\\n### Configuration Properties\\n\\n| Property&nbsp;Name | Property&nbsp;Description | Var&nbsp;Type | Default&nbsp;Value | Is&nbsp;Required |\\n|---|---|---|---|---|\\n| message | The message that will appear in the debug console | STRING |  | Yes |\\n\\n## Track Event\\n\\nTrack this event in Tag Manager's analytics\\n\\n### Configuration Properties\\n\\n| Property&nbsp;Name | Property&nbsp;Description | Var&nbsp;Type | Default&nbsp;Value | Is&nbsp;Required |\\n|---|---|---|---|---|\\n| event | Name of the event to be tracked | STRING |  | Yes |\\n| event_group | Name of the event group that is associated with this event | STRING |  | No |\"}")}}]);